SUMMARY:🔥 US Fed: FOMC Press Conference
DESCRIPTION:Source: US Fed\nImpact: high\nOfficial Federal Reserve monthl
 y calendar FOMC press conference entry.\n\nExplainer:\n• What it is: C
 entral Bank Rate Decision\n\n• Measures: Interest-rate decision\, poli
 cy statement and guidance from the central bank.\n\n• Usual market eff
 ect: More hawkish-than-expected guidance is usually bullish for the loca
 l currency and bearish for bonds. More dovish-than-expected guidance is 
 usually bearish for the currency and bullish for bonds.\n\n• Why trade
 rs care: Central-bank decisions directly affect interest rates\, currenc
 y valuation\, bond yields and equity risk appetite.\n\n• Frequency: Sc
 heduled several times per year.\n\n• Notes: The market often reacts no
 t only to the rate decision\, but also to the statement\, forecasts\, pr
 ess conference and tone.\n\n• Acronyms: FOMC = Federal Open Market Com
 mittee\; RBA = Reserve Bank of Australia.\n\nOfficial source: https://ww
 w.federalreserve.gov/newsevents/2026-july.htm
